About This Company
Since being established 230 years ago in Japan, this small enterprise has grown into a global pharmaceutical company that has earned the trust of our stakeholders, expanded our operations, and developed our own unique set of strengths.Our strengths lie in our ability to continually adapt to shifting market demands. We consistently provide physicians and patients with high-quality medicines, while acting with integrity in every aspect of our business.
